results.description:
White Rock lake, Sunset Bay
Shades Of Copper & Silver
A 2nd juvenile was behind the first and was showing off the pretty colors in the wings.  Adults will be solid black but the juveniles have wing feathers with a mix of black, copper and silver.    And another pair of pretty blue eyes.
